         }}
      }}
   }}
}}

菊頭蝠科僅有菊頭蝠屬一個現生的屬，兩者均為[[單系群|單系群]]，截至2019年菊頭蝠屬下共有106種物種，為蝙蝠中物種次多的屬（僅次於[[鼠耳蝠屬|鼠耳蝠屬]]），且有學者認為漠南非洲還有許多未被描述的菊頭蝠屬物種，有研究顯示當地可能有多達12個隱存種。另外，本屬許多物種可能沒有明顯的遺傳分歧，故應視為同種，例如{{le|卡胡茲菊頭蝠|Rhinolophus kahuzi}}與{{le|魯文佐里菊頭蝠|Rhinolophus ruwenzorii}}；{{link-uk|戈隆戈薩菊頭蝠|Rhinolophus gorongosae}}、{{le|羅德西亞菊頭蝠|Roberts' horseshoe bat}}與{{le|北非菊頭蝠|Bushveld horseshoe bat}}；以及{{le|史密瑟氏菊頭蝠|Smithers's horseshoe bat}}、{{le|柯恩氏菊頭蝠|Cohen's horseshoe bat}}與{{le|馬布菊頭蝠|Mount Mabu horseshoe bat}}等<ref name="Demos">{{cite journal |doi=10.1186/s12862-019-1485-1 |pmid=31434566 |pmc=6704657 |title=Molecular phylogenetics of the African horseshoe bats (Chiroptera: Rhinolophidae): Expanded geographic and taxonomic sampling of the Afrotropics |journal=BMC Evolutionary Biology |volume=19 |issue=1 |page=166 |year=2019 |last1=Demos |first1=Terrence C. |last2=Webala |first2=Paul W. |last3=Goodman |first3=Steven M. |last4=Kerbis Peterhans |first4=Julian C. |last5=Bartonjo |first5=Michael |last6=Patterson |first6=Bruce D.}}</ref>。除菊頭蝠屬外，本科還有一個已[[滅絕|滅絕]]的[[屬|屬]]''{{le|Palaeonycteris}}''，生存年代為{{le|早中新世|Early Miocene}}，其化石在法國[[圣热朗勒皮|圣热朗勒皮]]出土<ref>{{cite book|url=https://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/page/17771084|page=13|title=Catalogue of the Fossil Mammalia in the British Museum, (Natural History): The orders Primates, Chiroptera, Insectivora, Carnivora, and Rodentia|publisher=Order of the Trustees|year=1885|first=Richard|last=Lydekker|author-link=Richard Lydekker|access-date=2021-06-10|archive-date=2021-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210610085513/https://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/page/17771084|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | last1= Bogdanowicz | first1= W. | last2= Owen | first2= R. D. | year= 1992 | title= Phylogenetic analyses of the bat family Rhinolophidae | journal= Journal of Zoological Systematics and Evolutionary Research | volume= 30 | issue= 2 | page= 152 | url= http://www.faunaparaguay.com/rhino.pdf | quote= The sole fossil  genus, ''Palaeonycteris'', is known from the  Miocene of Europe (Heller 1936; Sigb and Legendre 1983; Hand 1984; cf. Simpson 1945 and Hall 1989) | doi= 10.1111/j.1439-0469.1992.tb00164.x | access-date= 2021-06-10 | archive-date= 2017-08-08 | archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20170808185604/http://www.faunaparaguay.com/rhino.pdf | dead-url= no }}</ref>。

==與人類關係==
===病毒自然宿主===
====冠狀病毒====
{{Bar chart
